                           <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Name of ANSI/ASHRAE Standard 62.2-2022 weather station for climate zone</xs:documentation>
                           
                           
                           <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Calculated field: If A02_ResidentialBuildingType == NonDwellingUnit result = N/A stored in NotApplicableMessage Else If parent document is CF1R-PRF-01 reference value from it but allow user to override it.  If not overriden, result is stored in B05_WeatherStationANSI_ASHRAE; Else if user overrides CF1R-PRF-01  value Or parent is CF1R-NCB-01 or CF1F-ADD-01, user selects from list based on value in A09_ClimateZone and this is stored in B05_WeatherStationCZ# where # is the climate zone; </xs:documentation>
                           
                        
                        </xs:annotation>
                        
                     
